    "description_long": "This is a yellow diamond-shaped road sign with the bold black text 'ROUGH ROAD' displayed in all capital letters. The sign is mounted on a tall, slender, and slightly bent metallic post, which gives it a distinctive wavy appearance. The sign's surface appears weathered, with some subtle wear and dirt, suggesting outdoor use. The back of the sign is plain and unmarked, while the sides reveal the thinness of the metal plate. The post is metallic gray, contrasting with the yellow sign, and is likely made of galvanized steel for durability. This type of sign is commonly found on roads to warn drivers of uneven or damaged pavement ahead.",
